snippet.title: Rocket League® - Chaos Run DLC Trailer
snippet.description: Welcome back to the Wasteland! Our new "Chaos Run" DLC Pack brings the post-apocalypse to Rocket League with two all-new vehicles, six unique Decals for each new Battle-Car (12 total), two new Paint Types, two new Wheels, two new Rocket Trails, three new Toppers, and three new Antennas!
